N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 16.9 - Collateral deposited with the comptroller to secure moneys on deposit

State Regulations

State agencies shall notify the Comptroller immediately, where the amount on deposit exceeds the collateral pledged with the Comptroller
as security therefor. Notes
